            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nR _ {x} (\\theta) \\equiv \\exp (- i \\frac {\\theta}{2} X) = \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} I - i \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} X = \\left( \\begin{array}{c c} \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} & - i \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} \\\\ - i \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} & \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} \\end{array} \\right) (1 7. 1)\n\\]"
