                0.855,
                0.294
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nR _ {y} (\\theta) \\equiv \\exp (- i \\frac {\\theta}{2} Y) = \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} I - i \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} Y = \\left( \\begin{array}{c c} \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} & - \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} \\\\ \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} & \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} \\end{array} \\right) \\tag {17.2}\n\\]"
        },
        {
