                0.335
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nR _ {z} (\\theta) \\equiv \\exp (- i \\frac {\\theta}{2} Z) = \\cos \\frac {\\theta}{2} I - i \\sin \\frac {\\theta}{2} Z = \\left( \\begin{array}{c c} \\exp (- i \\frac {\\theta}{2}) & 0 \\\\ 0 & \\exp (i \\frac {\\theta}{2}) \\end{array} \\right) (1 7. 3)\n\\]"
