            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\nR _ {x} (\\theta) | 0 \\rangle = \\left( \\begin{array}{c c} \\cos {\\frac {\\theta}{2}} & - i \\sin {\\frac {\\theta}{2}} \\\\ - i \\sin {\\frac {\\theta}{2}} & \\cos {\\frac {\\theta}{2}} \\end{array} \\right) \\binom{1}{0} = \\binom{\\cos {\\frac {\\theta}{2}}}{- i \\sin {\\frac {\\theta}{2}}} \\tag {17.5}\n\\]"
